r size=1> what should i expect from these vampyres in the fight <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon3.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/utabbran.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Tabbran</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/anim_1.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(1/2/02 2:02:32 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousethebackroomsecretsspoilers.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=9305.topic&index=7>Reply</a>    <br>Community Supporter<br> </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: .</span><hr size=1> They rampage and flurry, will try to gate at low hitpoints.<br><br>Immune to snare and root, otherwise have low fire and magic resistance. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2f2f4f><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/uironarse.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Ironarse</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(1/2/02 10:49:31 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousethebackroomsecretsspoilers.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=9305.topic&index=8>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: .</span><hr size=1>  I killed these monkeys for 15 hours the other day and havent seen gloves yet . Shoulders belt boots bracers drop good pp loot crowns ruby rings diamonds blue diamonds there is also a rare named spawn Emperor oomogo or some such looks like one of the hooded wraith men he droped a pair of nifty shadow step right click boots not sure on cast time and i forget the name also they drop kashar katar i think thats